      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a dedicated restoration project. The engine struggles to start and runs very poorly, indicating the need for major mechanical repairs or a complete overhaul. The exterior shows heavy wear with significant rust patches and faded paint, while the interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to tow this vehicle from the lot, as it is not currently in a reliable state for driving.",
